title: Selected Short Stories
creator: P. G. Wodehouse
description: LibriVox recording of Selected Short Stories, by P.G.Wodehouse. Read by Mike Harris A miscellaneous collection of short stories, not featuring any of Wodehouse's regular characters, most concern love and romance and, being Wodehouse, all are amusing.(Summary by Wikipedia) For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. M4B format available
subject: Audiobook;LibriVox;Fiction;Humor;short story;English
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text

reviews.reviewbody:
PL'd this and I spent a lot of time laughing out loud.  Not a good idea when you are in an office, oh well.

Mike H is an awesome reader.  You will love this collection.  Enjoy!
I'm a Wodehouse fan, but had not heard these stories before; a big thank you to the reader!
